{"tid":2391233,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"做給習主席看的封區大戲（余德寶）","createTime":"2021-02-02T05:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T05:39:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe8f90dc1e178776494f9f1a72e9ed20094d79c","tid":2391233,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/53US6JKSSFD63PMNM7YCHUYJHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2F53US6JKSSFD63PMNM7YCHUYJHU%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=41999ee8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2F53US6JKSSFD63PMNM7YCHUYJHU%2F&h=b44c3cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/53US6JKSSFD63PMNM7YCHUYJHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n做給習主席看的封區大戲（余德寶）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zBzr8N-mNHQN2kME7un4rKWNN5w=/1587x1000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BLUS4HHCJZFMLBWSMVT7O4AHSQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzBzr8N-mNHQN2kME7un4rKWNN5w%3D%2F1587x1000%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBLUS4HHCJZFMLBWSMVT7O4AHSQ.gif&h=0ed04d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭欠封區居民一個道歉，欠商戶和受影響市民一個賠償。政。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭和張建宗到訪被封區域做政治公關，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n三個被封區在解封之後，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漠視民意 從未與區議會溝通<br />\n<br />\n政府在抗疫政策，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府明言會檢討封區的成效，他們的確要檢討三次封區是否真的有減少疫情擴散，勞民傷財最後合共只尋到14位確診者。還是封區只為暗中令政府權力變成更大呢？如今已抗疫一年，林鄭表示自己工作盡心盡力，力保不失。一年前，醫護人員為了希望政府封關而罷工，卻被林鄭指摘玩政治。回顧過去，反看一海之隔的澳門，正因果斷封關而生活如常。香港市民卻要因為政府抗疫失敗而多次接受懲罰。當我們失去了100多條寶貴的性命、失去那麼多的經濟發展、就業機會，特首竟還說得出力保不失，香港人真是要自求多福。<br />\n<br />\n余德寶<br />\n<br />\n油尖旺區議會副主席"}]}